    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi.<persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/32"> Karolus</persName> gratia Dei
                        magnus <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus anni imperio eius (in
                        Francia) noni, in Italia anno primo, die nonum mense augusto, indictione
                        decima. Placuit adque convenit [in]ter <persName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus #Conductores"><name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martino</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldeo </rs><rs key="#Queen"
                            >domne</rs>
                        <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/55">Anchelberge</persName> Dea dicata
                        relicta quondam <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Hluduvici
                        </persName>imperatori nec non et inter <persName key="#Actionarii/actores"
                                ><name ref="Maginfredus">Manifre</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Maginfredus">Manifri</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Actionarii/actores"><name ref="Rainbertus"
                                >Rimpetto</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petroni</name></persName>, quia una per ipsius Petroni genitori suo
                        consensum et da[ta] licencia veluti <rs key="#Freeborn">hominis
                        liberis</rs>, ut in Dei nomine firmare et firmo ego qui supra Martino
                        gastaldio vobis suprascriptis Manifre Rimperto vel vestris heredibus<rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"> libellario nomine</rs> in casaes
                        vel rebus domne Anchelberge<rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Size"> in
                            iugis vigenti et quinque in ipses cases vel rebus</rs>, quod iam ante
                        hos dies per <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> et
                        Manifre genitor tuus Manifri iste sue <rs>l(a)borates </rs>fuerunt, in
                        medietatem firmo te Manifre vel tuis heredibus et in alia medietatem te
                        Rimperto vel tuis heredibus, in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/435">Felline</placeName>. In tale vero tinore firmo vos ut
                        vel vestris heredes super ipses rebus resedere et laborare adque meliorare
                        debeatis, sine fraude vel nelicto, da odie usque ad anno vigenti et novem,
                        et exinde de suprascripte rebus reditum redere debeatis per omni anno
                        circu[li] in parte domnne Inchelberge in <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs><placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Agricultural_renders #Exenia #Operae #Angaria"
                            ref="#places/33">
                            <geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Agricultural_renders #Exenia #Operae #Angaria"
                                ref="#estates/40"> Vuardestalla</geogName>
                        </placeName>de <rs key="#Agricultural_renders"><rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                                >seligine et sigale et ordeo tercio, alio omne labure modio
                                quarto</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vinum tercio</rs></rs>, exenio vero per
                        anno uno in ipso<rs key="#Exenia"> exenio </rs><rs key="#Poultry">pulli
                            dui</rs>, <rs key="#Eggs">oves decem</rs>; ipso exenio in sancti
                        Propssperii dare debeatis; <rs key="#Operae">operes</rs> vero per anno
                        facere debeatis in ipsa curte Vuardestalla dies vigenti et tres, medietatem
                            cum<rs key="#Cows"> bovis </rs>et medietatem manuvelis; ipse operes cum
                            <rs key="#Public_exactions">annonam domnica</rs> faciatis, et de ipso
                        reditum facere debeatis per anno <rs key="#Angaria">angaria una</rs>; in
                        ipsa angaria modia sex usque ad curte ad<rs key="#Lakes"> laco</rs>, et si
                        expertati <placeName key="#Rivers">Pado </placeName>venerit, ut ipso loco
                        dilierit, ut ibi vivere nun posatis, exiatis inde foris sine omnem calomnia,
                        et abeatis<rs key="#Hay/fodder"> prado</rs> modia dua, sestaria quatuor et
                            <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables #Agricultural_renders">orto et rapas
                        </rs>undecim redatis, et hoc omnem suprascripto reditum battere et vege(re)
                        et consignare debeatis cum vestro disspendio per anno in suprascripta curte
                        et ad expletis annis exiatis e foris cum medietatem de movilia vestra et
                        medietatem in loco cispidem dimitatis. Pena vero inter se posuerunt ut, si
                        quis ex ipsis aut heredibus ipsorum Manifri et Rimpetti vel parentes domnne
                        Anchelberge et non cunpleverint omnia qualiter superius legitur et si exire
                        aut menare voluerit ante suprascriptis annis, tunc compona pars partis fìdem
                        servanti in <rs key="#Penalty">argentum solidos vigenti</rs>, et post pena
                        soluta presens libelli in sua manea fìrmitatem. Unde hos libello
                        conscriptus. Acto feliciter. Signum ++manuum Manifri et Rimpetti qui
                        similiter fieri [ro]gaverunt. a Signum + manus Petroni qui in une libello
                        cunsensi. Signum + + + manuum <persName><name ref="Gaoseremdus">Gaoseremdi
                            </name></persName>adque <persName><name ref="Offredus"
                            >Ofredoni</name></persName> fìlio <persName><name ref="Anzeuertus"
                                >Anzeverti</name></persName> et<persName><name ref="Leo"> Leoni
                            </name></persName>Scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Adalbrandus">Adelprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">scavino</rs>
                        postraditas complevi et dedi. </ab>
